::Prowl::

Prowl lands inside the Cybertronian FIre's docking bay, the shuttle 
landing near him. He walks over to the hatch and watches it over. 
Bending down, he picks up Firedrill and one of the other robots, 
lifting into the air and flying through the corridors of the CF. He 
reaches the CR room, putting Firedrill and the other robot into 
different CRs.
